 Wintour) 和脱口秀主持人艾伦·德杰尼勒斯 (Ellen DeGeneres)。</p><p>谈到前者，奥斯本说：“哦，她喜欢[科登]。她爱他。但谁喜欢安娜·温图尔呢？她做到了。我认为她是一个C字。” </p><figure id="attachment_3598663" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3598663" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3598663" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Osbourne@2000x1270.jpg" alt="莎朗·奥斯本 (Sharon Osbourne) 于 2023 年 11 月 23 日在英国伦敦 The Roundhouse 举行的首届滚石英国颁奖典礼上在后台摆姿势。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Osbourne@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Osbourne@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Osbourne@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Osbourne@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Osbourne@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Sharon-Osbourne@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3598663" class="wp-caption-text">莎朗·奥斯本 (Sharon Osbourne) 于 2023 年 11 月 23 日在英国伦敦 The Roundhouse 举行的首届滚石英国颁奖典礼上在后台摆姿势。 （戴夫·贝内特/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>在参加真人秀之前，奥斯本猛烈抨击<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·维斯特</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-osbourne-says-kanye-west-fucked-with-the-wrong-jew-this-time-3585447">称他“这次和错误的犹太人上床了”</a> 。该评论是在这位说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-hits-out-at-antisemite-kanye-west-for-using-war-pigs-sample-without-permission-3585240">未经乐队许可</a>在他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ty-dolla-ign">Ty Dolla $ign 合作的</a>专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-and-ty-dolla-ign-release-controversial-new-album-vultures-1-listen-spotify-tracklist-artwork-3585547">Vultures</a> 》中使用 Black Sabbath 样本后不久发表的。</p><p>在对韦斯特的批评中，她称他为“无礼的反犹太分子”，“代表着仇恨”。据报道，奥斯